# Tribulation tier-detail panel — 9-slice frame (slice inset = 6px)
# Neutral slate frame with crimson corner accents. Tier color is a
# programmatic accent; the centered skull watermark is drawn in code
# (a 9-slice center is stretched, so it cannot be baked here).
